== 評價和影響 ==
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]給予32%的新鮮度，認為這種低預算的殭屍電影大量借鑒了其他優秀的同類作品，既不原創也不夠娛樂<ref>{{cite web |title=Undead(2005) |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/undead_2003 |website=rottentomatoes |accessdate=2019-01-19 |archive-date=2021-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412035217/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/undead_2003 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]獲得34分，得到普遍不佳的評論<ref>{{cite web |title=UNDEAD |url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/undead/critic-reviews |website=metacritic |accessdate=2019-01-19 |archive-date=2020-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200403163720/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/undead/critic-reviews |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

不過，活屍入侵獲得2003年的[[費比西獎|費比西獎]]，被評「因為敢於成為澳大利亞電影一部分流行卻聲名狼藉的流派。我們稱讚它既是一種政治性的娛樂，同時又展現出熱衷製作電影的心」<ref>{{cite web |title=52nd Melbourne International Film Festival |url=http://www.fipresci.org/festival-reports/2003/melbourne-international-film-festival |website=fipresci prize |accessdate=2019-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190119120912/http://www.fipresci.org/festival-reports/2003/melbourne-international-film-festival |archive-date=2019-01-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。
